[{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"CurrentModule = TensorNetworkAD2","category":"page"},{"location":"#TensorNetworkAD2","page":"Home","title":"TensorNetworkAD2","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Documentation for TensorNetworkAD2.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Modules = [TensorNetworkAD2]","category":"page"},{"location":"#TensorNetworkAD2.StopFunction-Tuple{Any}","page":"Home","title":"TensorNetworkAD2.StopFunction","text":"(st::StopFunction)(state)\n\nstopfunction for ctmrg, returning true if singular values are converged or the maximum number of iterations is reached. Implemented as a closure since it needs to remember the last singular values it saw for comparison.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#TensorNetworkAD2.fixedpoint-Tuple{Any, Any, Any}","page":"Home","title":"TensorNetworkAD2.fixedpoint","text":"fixedpoint(f, guess, stopfun)\n\nreturn the result of applying guess = f(guess) until convergence. Convergence is decided by applying stopfun(guess) which returns a Boolean.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#TensorNetworkAD2.trg_i-Tuple{ITensors.ITensor}","page":"Home","title":"TensorNetworkAD2.trg_i","text":"trg(T::ITensor; χmax::Int, nsteps::Int) -> κ, T\n\nPerform the TRG algorithm on the partition function composed of the ITensor T.\n\nThe indices of T must obey come in pairs (sₕ => sₕ') and  `(sᵥ => sᵥ').\n\nχmax is the maximum renormalized bond dimension.\n\nnsteps are the number of renormalization steps performed.\n\nThe outputs are κ, the partition function per site, and the final renormalized ITensor T.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"}]
